WEBVTT

00:06:59.681 --> 00:07:04.309
Apu connotu unu giovunu, Emeka,
chi s'est amarmurau gioghendi a football.

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:07.379
A pustis de s'incidenti, Emeka at nau:

00:07:07.403 --> 00:07:10.108
"Sa vida mia fuet bella
gioghendi a football,

00:07:10.132 --> 00:07:12.256
ma castiaimiri imoi".

00:07:14.002 --> 00:07:16.294
Sa genti chi narat storias
cument'a custa --

00:07:16.318 --> 00:07:18.842
"Sa vida mia fuet bella,
imoi est legia".--

00:07:18.866 --> 00:07:21.688
tendint a essi prus apentzamentaus
e prus depressus.

00:07:21.712 --> 00:07:24.041
E Emeka fuet aici po unu pagu de tempus.

00:07:24.573 --> 00:07:27.964
Ma cun su tempus, at cumentzau
a tessi unu contu diferenti.

00:07:28.415 --> 00:07:30.148
Su contu nou fuet: